<p>Well, I have to say that I&#8217;m now in the 170s.</p>

<p>The system works.  The best thing about the Shangri-la diet is that you can try it without buying the book.</p>

<p>A friend called it the &#8220;try it first for free&#8221; diet, and then noted &#8220;if it works, you can just keep doing it for free.&#8221;  Not like you have to buy anything special, any light, flavor free oil or sugar will do, you can find all the instructions on-line.</p>

<p>It is fun to watch the diet ripple out among friends and family and hear them talk about how it changes how they feel about food.</p>

